Freelance Spy
A Freelance Spy sells information and intelligence to the highest bidder,
working without permanent affiliation to any single faction. In the Rifts
world of competing powers, a skilled spy with no loyalty is highly employable.

Freelance Spies choose from Espionage, Rogue, Technical, and Physical skill
categories. They are trained in surveillance, disguise, intelligence gathering,
and discreet communication. Combat is a last resort.

Attribute requirements: IQ 11, MA 10, PP 10.
Starting equipment: Concealed recording device, encrypted communicator, two
changes of civilian clothing, a concealed sidearm, forged credentials, and
working capital for bribes.
